@startuml 'title' 

!include https://raw.github.com/pandadoc-se/misc-pandadoc-puml/main/pandadoc_defaults.puml

autonumber

  Box PandaDoc
    actor User order 1
    participant Document order 2
    participant ProcessAutomations order 3
  end Box

skinparam actorBorderColor black
skinparam actorBackgroundColor DarkSeaGreen

  actor Employee order 4

  Box BambooHR #LightGray
    database EmployeeRecord order 5
  end Box

  User -> Document: Creates
  Document --> Document: link to Employee Record
  Document --> Document: Send
  Employee -> Document: Employee Signs

  group#LightGray #FFF7E3 monitor
    ProcessAutomations o<[#red]- Document : Status Changes to Complete
    autonumber stop
    EmployeeRecord <--[#red]o ProcessAutomations: Attach PDF 
  end

@enduml